title: Arbol Data Catalog
description: This catalog contains all the data uploaded to Arbol                 that has been issued STAC-compliant metadata. The catalogs and collections describe single providers.                 Each may contain one or multiple datasets. Each individual dataset has been documented as STAC Items.
